---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
  
<style>
  .content blockquote {
    background: transparent url(/images/content_horiz_divider.png) no-repeat left
      bottom;
    margin: 22px 0;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .content blockquote p {
    background: transparent url(/images/about_quote_bg.png) no-repeat left top;
    color: #e25a01;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.55em;
    padding: 8px 98px 0 98px;
    text-indent: 0;
  }

  #accreditations-memberships dt {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  #accreditations-memberships dt b {
    color: #f7dbb2;
    font-weight: normal;
    font-size: 40px;
    left: 105px;
    position: relative;
    top: 8px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  #accreditations-memberships dt span {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0px;
    top: 16px;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  #accreditations-memberships dt span.first-child {
    left: 0px;
    top: 0px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .content blockquote {
      margin: 18px 0;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .content blockquote p {
      background-image: url(/images/mobile_about_quote_bg.jpg);
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 0px 40px 0 50px;
    }

    #about-location .content-secondary {
      display: none;
    }

    #accreditations-memberships {
      padding: 0 6px 0 0;
    }

    #accreditations-memberships dt {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    #accreditations-memberships dt b {
      color: #9a5324;
      font-size: 18px;
      left: auto;
      position: relative;
      top: auto;
    }

    #accreditations-memberships dt span {
      position: relative;
      right: auto;
      top: auto;
    }

    #accreditations-memberships dt span.first-child {
      left: auto;
      top: auto;
    }

    #accreditations-memberships li {
      padding: 4px 0;
    }
  }
</style>

<BaseLayout bodyId="about">
  <div class="content first-child">
    <div class="content-main">
      <h2>Karma Gaw</h2>

      <blockquote>
        <p>
          I truly believe that the work I do is a gift and it is a pleasure
          to pass that gift on to my clients.
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        Karma is a Nationally Board Certified Licensed Massage Therapist. As
        well as an AFAA Personal Trainer and Licensed PiYo, Zumba, and
        “Strong” by Zumba instructor.
      </p>
      <p>
        Her background in bodyworks spans 20 years. In that time she has
        become a Certified Aerobic, Step, and Kickboxing Instructor and has
        also competed in National Aerobic Championships. As a Personal
        Trainer she has certified over 45 women to be instructors in the
        fitness industry. Twice she has appeared in American Fitness
        Magazine highlighting her achievements in fitness training.
      </p>
      <p>
        Karma believes that she was meant to be
        <strong>“Good Karma”</strong> through touch. She is very intuitive
        and truly believes massage allows the body to heal itself.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-secondary">
      <span class="picture-frame">
        <img
          src="/images/karmagaw-2022.jpg"
          alt="A portrait of Karma Gaw"
        />
      </span>
      <dl id="accreditations-memberships">
        <dt>
          <span class="first-child">Accreditations</span> <b>&amp;</b>
          <span>Memberships</span>
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>NCTMB</strong> <span>#518232-06</span></li>
            <li>
              <strong>AFAA Certified Personal Trainer PT</strong>
              <span>#592-3</span>
            </li>
            <li><strong>ABMP Member</strong></li>
          </ul>
        </dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content" id="about-location">
    <div class="content-main">
      <h2>Location</h2>
      <p>
        Massage is intended to be an immersive, relaxing experience. Not
        being in a city, surrounded by the noise of hustle and bustle of day
        to day life is paramount to a complete massage experience. Custom
        Body Works is a peaceful, quiet 5 miles outside of the nearest small
        town, Bowling Green Missouri. Here, you can fully relax and get the
        most out of your massage.

        <br /><br />Karma has been practicing at this location since
        October, 2007.
        <a href="contact" rel="contact" title="Directions"
          >Need help getting here?</a
        >
      </p>
      <ul class="photo-gallery">
        <li>
          <a
            class="fancybox"
            rel="gallery-photos"
            href="/images/gallery_building.jpg"
            ><img src="/images/gallery_building_thumb.jpg" alt="Exterior"
          /></a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="fancybox"
            rel="gallery-photos"
            href="/images/gallery_office.jpg"
            ><img src="/images/gallery_office_thumb.jpg" alt="Office"
          /></a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="fancybox"
            rel="gallery-photos"
            href="/images/gallery_workspace.jpg"
            ><img src="/images/gallery_workspace_thumb.jpg" alt="Workspace"
          /></a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="fancybox"
            rel="gallery-photos"
            href="/images/gallery_massageroom01.jpg"
            ><img
              src="/images/gallery_massageroom01_thumb.jpg"
              alt="Massage Room 01"
          /></a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="fancybox"
            rel="gallery-photos"
            href="/images/gallery_massageroom02.jpg"
            ><img
              src="/images/gallery_massageroom02_thumb.jpg"
              alt="Massage Room 02"
          /></a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-secondary">
      <span class="picture-frame">
        <img src="/images/about_location.jpg" alt="" />
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <span id="view-bottom"></span>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/jquery.fancybox-1.3.1.css" />
</BaseLayout>
